# Smart Waste Management

This project is built on Salesforce to manage smart waste collection.

## Features
- Register waste bins and collection points
- Track waste levels using sensors
- Assign collection trucks automatically
- Generate reports and dashboards in Salesforce

## Tech Stack
- Salesforce Apex
- LWC (Lightning Web Components)
- GitHub + VS Code
